- preserves the completed rule-registry baseline and direct coverage reporting;
- records the accepted rule-registry improvement backlog;
- prepares the repository for successor-chat closeout before resuming documentation-management work;
- includes release metadata, documentation, governance, test, lint, and package-build verification.

